node.text: Did you know I’m gogo dancing this Saturday, August 14th at @clubbarsinister ?? 🔥 Your chance to see me shake it in person! comment below if you would like to be added to my guest list to get in for FREE! Stoked about some of the opportunities I have had lately & that will be coming my way in the future. Been feeling stuck lately but a little jammin always helps. I gotta really push myself sometimes, but it always ends up being worth it. So if you’re feeling a little stuck, try to do at least one thing for yourself that takes a little bit of energy but makes you smile. For me, it was dancing just a tad. 😌

node.text: Let’s get bumpin! #freebritney For some reason the lighting went to shit when posting this? Weird but typical IG haha. Anyway - I honestly have so much fun with these lmao. Been posting these smokin’ dance videos for 4 or so years. I never really think about stopping cus they make me smile & laugh and it makes me happy when people say it does the same for them, especially when they say it makes them want to dance too hehe. I’m trying to get so much done today! I’ve been feeling really good about certain things lately but have been having a tough time with others! But it’s ok & I’m navigating them pretty well if I do say so myself. Life is life & that’s just how it is. I can appreciate certain things about myself like my ability to communicate, be open to other perspectives & allowing myself to grow in certain ways. Grateful for people & situations in my life that help me do so. Cus that’s what life is all about. Learning about yourself, allowing yourself to grow & figuring out how to navigate life without absolutely losing your shit and going completely off track hehehe. Wishing everyone well. In the good times & the bad ☀️

node.title: Watch til the end, promise you’ll smile 😅

node.text: There has been so much chaos since getting back home from vacation last month that I haven’t felt much like making my cute little dance videos. But, alas! Here I am. Headed out of town once again this weekend.. off to Oregon! I have never been & am very excited to enjoy nature while spending time with some friends hehe. Also, hello from my cowlick that never goes away 😅

node.text: Still here in Florida on vacation! I’ve been here for almost a week now. 😋 Heading back to Phoenix in a few days. Having such an amazing time with myself, this was the best decision ever! I have so many new photoshoots coming up, lots of new sets for my fans (so be sure to jo¡n my page!) and a nice little tan too hehe. Plus, my new @suicidegirls set comes out in a little less than 2 days! Overall a great fucking week 😀💚 I have so much more to share about my trip, but I will wait until I’m home. There’s just so much I’ve been doing hehe. Keep up with me in my stories & on my other social media too! Including the over 18 stuff.. you know you know.

node.text: Having fun as always hehe. Hope you are too! I’m taking a vacation to Florida next week and I am so excited. (: I have a couple shoots planned, meeting some fellow SG’s and am going to spend lots of time on the beach! I’ll be checking out a few museums, taking lots of photos & eating some good food! I am ready as all hell to treat myself hehe. If you’re in the FL area, let me know! I’ll be traveling a few different cities while there. 💚✨🌴 Any trips planned? Favorite places to go? Exciting long weekend? Tell me about it :)

node.text: Feeling really good lately! Ever since I quit my job I feel like a complete ~me~ again. It’s nice ☺️ I’ve had so much more time to myself and have been keeping myself so busy this week! Finally cracking down on getting my house together & set to begin some of my new projects for my art venture! I’m excited to share my page with you soon, but want to make sure I actually have some stuff to share first hehe :) So just keep a look out for some announcements about some of the art & things I will be doing! I’ve always wanted to create alternative home decor and I’m way stoked to actually be taking the risk to do it! I’m headed out of the house to grab more supplies as I type this 😋 Have you completed any projects lately? 💚

node.text: I ran a few errands today, took some photos & posted them on my fän pge and am taking my dog to the park after I each some lunch :) I’ve been spending a lot of time getting my office in my house together so I have some organization when I start getting into making some art and thingsss. I’ve definitely been able to take care of a lot of little things around the house I wasn’t able to, so I’m definitely using my time wisely :) Thankfully I’ve been able to find a nice balance of productivity and relaxation which is important of course hehe. How has everyone else been feeling?

node.text: Hehehe. Hope you did at least one thing today that makes you happy! Happiness is what I strive for and honestly what I try to live by. 🤷🏻‍♀️ What’s life without happiness, right? There’s a few things missing but you make the most out of what you got so long as it ain’t shitty. 😅 And if it is then do your best to change it if you can. If you can’t, try to worry less. Easier said than done, but weee can do it!

node.text: You have no restrictions when it’s just yoouuu so you may as well let loose, you know? Of course I guess this is a poor example as I am sharing it with the world and I guess am no longer doing this alone 😂 Have a great weekend!! What are the plans? I’m headed to Sedona with some ladies, hopefully taking the bike out for a bit, doing some art and we will see what else finagles it’s way into my calendar.

node.text: Some behind the scenes clips taken from my @suicidegirls live stream of @alissa_brunelli shooting my new SuicideGirls set back in December! The set will be live on the site in just 3 months!! I’m super excited for this set and will share an official preview photo from the set in a few weeks! This video isn’t the best quality hehe but if you’d like to watch the full stream, view my other sets & not miss my new set when it’s published make sure to sign up using my I¡nk or by clicking through my ‘SG🍒💣’ highlight reel on my profile :)

node.text: I bought this backdrop stand and finally put it up so I can set up some different things for photos & such! I’ve been having a chill day so far :) Nice balance between relaxing and getting things done. It’s been nice! I haven’t posted on my page in nearly a month and I think that’s the longest I’ve gone.. I post on my story pretty much every day but it’s been a long while for my page haha.  I needed a break anyway to reboost my engagement I think hehe. We’ll see how it goes! Comment below one thing you have done or hope to do this weekend! Save this post if you need a little boogie boost every once in awhile :)

Tomorrow night I will be making my dancing debut at @clubbarsinister🌹 Have a few spots left for my guest list, comment below to be added for complimentary entry as a thank you for coming out to see me. Celebrating my birthday a little early - come join, treat me, bring me a rose perhaps? If you can’t make it there’s always next time! If you’d like to still send a gift my wishlist is available alongside other access points in the info section on my profile.

node.text: Did you know I’m gogo dancing this Saturday, August 14th at @clubbarsinister ?? 🔥 Your chance to see me shake it in person! comment below if you would like to be added to my guest list to get in for FREE! Stoked about some of the opportunities I have had lately & that will be coming my way in the future. Been feeling stuck lately but a little jammin always helps. I gotta really push myself sometimes, but it always ends up being worth it. So if you’re feeling a little stuck, try to do at least one thing for yourself that takes a little bit of energy but makes you smile. For me, it was dancing just a tad. 😌

node.text: Let’s get bumpin! #freebritney For some reason the lighting went to shit when posting this? Weird but typical IG haha. Anyway - I honestly have so much fun with these lmao. Been posting these smokin’ dance videos for 4 or so years. I never really think about stopping cus they make me smile & laugh and it makes me happy when people say it does the same for them, especially when they say it makes them want to dance too hehe. I’m trying to get so much done today! I’ve been feeling really good about certain things lately but have been having a tough time with others! But it’s ok & I’m navigating them pretty well if I do say so myself. Life is life & that’s just how it is. I can appreciate certain things about myself like my ability to communicate, be open to other perspectives & allowing myself to grow in certain ways. Grateful for people & situations in my life that help me do so. Cus that’s what life is all about. Learning about yourself, allowing yourself to grow & figuring out how to navigate life without absolutely losing your shit and going completely off track hehehe. Wishing everyone well. In the good times & the bad ☀️

node.text: Making magic ✨ My trip in Oregon has been quite an experience! One I very much appreciate. Heading back home to Phoenix tomorrow evening but I think I will find my way back here again in the near future. ☺️ I have so many new photos I am excited to see & share. When I get back home I am ready to get back to my overly ambitious self where I dominate my own world within this crazy one we are all trying to navigate. I am magic & all my dreams will come true, because I want them too. ✨

node.text: Currently in Oregon on another adventure. My stories are the best way to enjoy me in real time as I am not the best with keeping up my actual page to accurately reflect what is always happening at the time. Enjoy a snippet of a shoot from the spring - what it feels like it is in Oregon right now. 😅 Enjoying my time in new places, but always looking forward to being back in the desert.☀️

node.text: Here is the first of many random collections of photos from my Florida vacation.😀 This was my first night there in Miami. I got a cute little place to stay a short walk from the beach! Immediately changed into my bikini after getting off the plane and settling in aka putting my bags down & rolling a blunt. Headed to the beach where I hung out a bit, took some photos & collected some sea shells! Seen some dudes killin it while kiteboarding (?) it is apparently called lol. Where they’re on a board with the big ol parachute! Wild. You can see it a little itty bit in the second to last photo hehe. I’m guna be sharing more photos over time, it was so much fun. I’m so glad I took my solo vacation. It was a blast and the best idea, are you kidding meeee!? The view was beautiful, I haven’t been to the ocean that many times and I love the saaannddd. I never shared much about it on my page other than on my stories. So I’ll just relive it every once in awhile as I gradually share my memories haha.

node.text: There has been so much chaos since getting back home from vacation last month that I haven’t felt much like making my cute little dance videos. But, alas! Here I am. Headed out of town once again this weekend.. off to Oregon! I have never been & am very excited to enjoy nature while spending time with some friends hehe. Also, hello from my cowlick that never goes away 😅
